CustomField.description: The date that shows the most recent Contract End/Anniversary Date. This shows the Original CEA Date before renewal and once renewed the current CEA Date.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This shows the Original CEA Date before renewal and once renewed the current CEA Date. This will be set upon initial entry of the CEA Date - Original value. *For manual renewals, please set this to the new CEA Date for man. renewal.
CustomField.label: CEA Date - Active
